{"comments":"Portal system for layered rendering — Pure Data\n\nPortals model **content that renders at a different layer** from its\nlogical position in the component tree. This is pure data describing\nlayering intent; the runtime interprets it for actual rendering.\n\n## Pure Data Model\n\nInstead of imperative DOM manipulation, portals are described as:\n\n1. **LayerLevel** — Which layer to render to (z-index tier)\n2. **PortalContent** — What to render in the portal\n3. **StackingContext** — The current state of all layers\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Portal.Layer as Portal\n\n-- Define a modal that renders in the Modal layer\nmyModal :: forall msg. Model -> Portal.PortalContent msg\nmyModal model =\n  Portal.portalContent\n    { level: Portal.Modal\n    , key: \"my-modal\"\n    , trapFocus: true\n    , ariaLabel: Just \"Confirmation dialog\"\n    }\n    [ modalContent model ]\n\n-- In your view, portals are collected at the top level\nview :: Model -> Element msg\nview model = \n  Portal.withPortals\n    [ when model.showModal (myModal model) ]\n    (mainContent model)\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[94,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[94,3]},"title":"Base"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[95,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[95,3]},"title":"Dropdown"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[96,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[96,3]},"title":"Sticky"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[97,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[97,3]},"title":"Popover"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[98,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[98,3]},"title":"Modal"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[99,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[99,3]},"title":"Toast"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[100,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[100,3]},"title":"Tooltip"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[101,3]},"title":"Overlay"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[102,3]},"title":"Custom"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Portal","Layer"],"LayerLevel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[104,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[104,1]},"title":"eqLayerLevel"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Portal","Layer"],"LayerLevel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[107,56],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Portal/Layer.purs","start":[106,1]},"title":"ordLayerLevel"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Portal","Layer"],"LayerLevel"],"tag":"TypeConstruc